org.livingdoc.repositories.confluence

Class ConfluenceRepositoryFactory

  • org.livingdoc.repositories.confluence.ConfluenceRepositoryFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentRepositoryFactory<T>

    public class ConfluenceRepositoryFactory
implements DocumentRepositoryFactory<T>

    This Factory is used to create a ConfluenceRepository. This Factory must be specified in the livingdoc.yml to use the Confluence Repository. For more details about the {@see ConfluenceRepository} see it's documentation.
